elements.name: To validate the qoute creation SME distributor

steps.name: User must be in the login page
User enter valid emailId and password
User must be in the home page
User must be in the create qoute page
User click company details next button
User select start date and end date in census
User should click and upload template
User must displayed with quote created popup message
User should validate the total premium for the created qoute

name: To Validate the create quote feature of distributor SME application
